text: Keanu Kole Baccus (born 7 June 1998) is a South African-born Australian soccer player. He plays for St Mirren in the Scottish Premiership and for the Australia men's national soccer team (nicknamed the "Socceroos"). ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Australian men's soccer players Category:South African soccer players Category:Sportspeople from Durban Category:2022 FIFA World Cup players
